{"tid":1643322,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好攞呢啲野黎玩喇","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T11:14:25.000Z","uid":137043,"like":521,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"a3fd6f4a470c75f90a333e09fddc610cba402073","tid":1643322,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:35:21.000Z","msg":"記得前排連登好似有人講起唔好用momo黎做文宣<br />\n幾個月後喺浸大啲樓梯底見到三四張<br />\n近距離到覺得自己就黎錫到momo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾張都算喇dup低頭唔望咪無事<br />\n啊屌你老母呢幾日啲momo文宣痴到周圍都係<br />\n啲必經路嘅牆身同電梯都痴哂momo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次見到都走避不及唔敢望，夜少少經過見到仲驚<br />\n到依家我都唔夠膽仔細望張文宣係講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信唔少人同我一樣都驚驚地隻垃圾毛毛<br />\n整完岀黎咁恐怖有幾多人會肯停低研究？<br />\n不如唔好再用佢黎做文宣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同場運動又無關<br />\n嚇親人又做唔到宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上圖一張<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etdGj7A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetdGj7A.png&h=e795eb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係好恐怖...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc9191db6261e32ee6f6cf7aca139e6c87ba7d2","tid":1643322,"uid":137043,"like":17,"dislike":6,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"無人驚momo？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbe0e58287cac98ab8f4c13eef6cab8b298aee1","tid":1643322,"uid":137043,"like":40,"dislike":5,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:43:18.000Z","msg":"仲有大把選擇但唔好用momo喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0acc4000bf30583cae833d76503a19e0e9d4f0","tid":1643322,"uid":137043,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:43:30.000Z","msg":"今晚會發惡